---
layout: base.njk
title: Articles
description: Ressources et analyses sur la gestion de domaine vitivinicole — par Teddy Pereira.
permalink: /articles/
---

<section class="about-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section__label" style="color:rgba(244,237,217,0.6)">Ressources</p>
    <h1 style="color:var(--cream)">Articles</h1>
    <p style="color:rgba(244,237,217,0.8); font-style:italic; margin:0; font-size:1.05rem;">
      Du terrain. Du concret. Pas de théorie.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    {% if collections.posts | length > 0 %}
    <div class="articles-grid">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <div class="article-card">
        {% if post.data.pilier %}
        <p class="article-card__pilier">{{ post.data.pilier }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="article-card__title">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
        {% if post.data.description %}
        <p class="article-card__excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <p class="article-card__meta">{{ post.date | dateReadable }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    {% else %}
    <p style="color:var(--muted); font-style:italic; text-align:center; padding: 3rem 0;">
      Les premiers articles arrivent bientôt.<br>
      <a href="/#waitlist">Rejoindre la liste d'attente →</a>
    </p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
